OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,FA man whose identical twin brother was
OL,7,Fmurdered by two teenagers says while
OL,8,Fhe cannot forgive them for what they
OL,9,Fdid he believes they have been
OL,10,Fpunished enough - and deserve a second
OL,11,Fchance.
OL,13,FSimon Dawson was killed in 1998 after
OL,14,Fbeing confronted by teenagers Craig
OL,15,FRoberts and Carl Harrison in
OL,16,FBrotherton Park in Bromborough, in
OL,17,FWirral.
