OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,FHe was stamped on and knocked
OL,7,Funconscious, before the pair then
OL,8,Fthrew him in the lake where he died
OL,9,Ffrom drowning.
OL,11,FRoberts, 16, and Harrison, 19, then
OL,12,Ftook Simon's bank card and withdrew
OL,13,Fmoney from a machine.
OL,15,FHis identical twin Nick did all he
OL,16,Fcould to help the Merseyside Police
OL,17,Finvestigation which followed, and in
OL,18,FJuly 1999 the pair were convicted and
OL,19,Freceived life sentenced.
