OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,FDespite his grief and anger Nick met
OL,7,FRoberts in person in prison in 2015
OL,8,Fwhere he says he saw a man "deeply
OL,9,Fashamed" of what he had done, and his
OL,10,F"horrific upbringing created a monster
OL,11,Fcapable of violence".
OL,13,FNick says meeting Roberts helped him
OL,14,Faccept but not forgive what had
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,F"It's been a very important part of my
OL,18,Fjourney, I've spent so many years
OL,19,Ftrying to find meaning in what
OL,20,Fhappened, and trying to get some
OL,21,Funderstanding and acceptance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
