OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,F"The meeting with Craig, the youngest
OL,7,Foffender, came about after I attended
OL,8,Fhim parole hearing.
OL,10,F"It was an incredibly powerful session
OL,11,Fwhere I was able to truly understand
OL,12,Fhim, truly understand the crime and
OL,13,Fhear him express his remorse and
OL,14,Fsorrow for what he had done."
OL,16,FNick speaks to Granada Reports
OL,17,Fpresenters Andy Bonner and Katie
OL,18,FWalderman about his brother - and his
OL,19,Ffeelings about the offenders
