OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,FNow, 27 years later, one of Simon's
OL,7,Fkillers is out of prison, while the
OL,8,Fother is bidding for freedom after
OL,9,Fbeing sent back to jail twice.
OL,11,FNick accepts they should both be given
OL,12,Ftheir freedom, but says he cannot
OL,13,Fforgive them. He recently attended
OL,14,FHarrison's parole hearing.
OL,16,F"It's been a long time for me, it's
OL,17,Falong journey, it's 27 years now since
OL,18,Fwe lost Simon," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
