OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,F"I'm ready, and have been ready for
OL,7,Fsome time, about accepting their
OL,8,Frelease. This parole hearing
OL,9,F(Harrison's) is about telling him I'm
OL,10,Fokay for him to come out of prison.
OL,12,F"I personally had to get to that
OL,13,Fjourney of accepting their freedom so
OL,14,FI can live at peace with what
OL,15,Fhappened."
OL,17,FHe says while he is ready to accept
OL,18,Fthe reality of what happened, he is
OL,19,Fnot yet ready to forgive the killers.
