OL,6,FNick added he believes they both
OL,7,Fdeserve a second change.
OL,9,F"They spent a very long time in prison
OL,10,Fand having been to their parole
OL,11,Fhearings and having met one of them I
OL,12,Fjust feel that it's a wasted life for
OL,13,Fthem to spend the rest of their lives
OL,14,Fin prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
