OL,3,CMan says his twin's killers deserve a
OL,4,Csecond chance
OL,6,F"I've had that connection and I've
OL,7,Fbeen able to get answer and
OL,8,Funderstand, I wanted to get to a
OL,9,Fposition of accepting their freedom -
OL,10,Fit was so important for my life,
OL,11,Fespecially as I've got a long time
OL,12,Fstill to live."
OL,14,FDescribing his brother he said the
OL,15,Flived an idyllic childhood in West
OL,16,FCumbria - he said because they were
OL,17,Fidentical they had a very close bond.
OL,19,F"He was my life long companion, and I
OL,20,Fwas very sad to lose him," Nick added.
